<name>DRIVE LINE</name>
<section id="1000K_S000I" variety="S000I">
<name>DIFFERENTIAL</name>
<ttl id="1000K_S000I_7A7ZV_T0049" variety="T0049">
<name>DIFFERENTIAL OIL</name>
<para id="RM0000037HK00LX" category="A" type-id="30019" name-id="DF137-01" from="201202">
<name>REPLACEMENT</name>
<subpara id="RM0000037HK00LX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000037HK00LX_01_0001" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000056K00000">
<ptxt>DRAIN DIFFERENTIAL OIL</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Stop the vehicle on a level surface.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the differential filler plug and gasket.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the drain plug and gasket, and drain the oil.  </ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install a new gasket and the drain plug.  </ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>49</t-value1>
<t-value2>500</t-value2>
<t-value4>36</t-value4>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000037HK00LX_01_0002" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000056L00000">
<ptxt>ADD DIFFERENTIAL OIL</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Add differential oil so that the oil level is within 5 mm (0 to 0.196 in.) from the bottom lip of the differential filler plug hole.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="D025304E51" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<table>
<title>Text in Illustration</title>
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="0.41in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="3.72in"/>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>*a</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>0 to 5 mm (0 to 0.196 in.)</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<atten3>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>After changing the oil, drive the vehicle, and then check the oil level again.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Too much or too little oil will lead to differential problems.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten3>
<ptxt>If necessary, fill the differential carrier with hypoid gear oil.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Differential oil type</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>Hypoid gear oil API GL-5</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>Recommended Viscosity</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.07in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="2.06in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Temperature</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>Viscosity</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Above -18째C (0째F)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>SAE 90</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>Below -18째C (0째F)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>SAE 80W-90 or SAE 80W</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>Standard Rear Differential Oil Capacity</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>3.00 to 3.10 liters (2.84 to 2.93 US qts., 2.64 to 2.73 Imp. qts.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check for oil leakage when the oil level is low.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install a new gasket and the differential filler plug.</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>49</t-value1>
<t-value2>500</t-value2>
<t-value4>36</t-value4>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
